OL,3,CSchool security reviewed after knife
OL,4,Cassault
OL,6,FA "full security audit" has been
OL,7,Fcarried out at Jersey's Haute Vallee
OL,8,FSchool after a knife assault left one
OL,9,Fstudent with minor injuries.
OL,11,FThe incident happened on Monday
OL,12,Flunchtime in the secondary school's
OL,13,Fcanteen (9 February) and a 14-year-old
OL,14,Fboy was held down by staff until the
OL,15,Fpolice arrived and arrested him.
OL,17,FIn a public letter on Tuesday,
OL,18,Fheadteacher Stuart Hughes sought to
OL,19,Freassure parents and address their
OL,20,Fconcerns over safety, as well as how
OL,21,Fthe incident was handled.
