OL,6,FHe wrote: "Our absolute priority today
OL,7,Fhas been to ensure that all students
OL,8,Fand colleagues attending school feel
OL,9,Fsafe, supported, and well.
OL,11,F"Students who felt understandably
OL,12,Foverwhelmed were offered additional
OL,13,Fsupport ... Staff have also been
OL,14,Foffered similar support.
OL,16,F"We also met with the Education
OL,17,FDepartment Health and Safety Team, who
OL,18,Fcarried out a full security audit of
OL,19,Fthe school site.
