OL,6,F"We will respond promptly to any
OL,7,Frecommendations arising from this
OL,8,Freview, and I will continue to monitor
OL,9,Fthis situation closely over this week
OL,10,Fand next to ensure that any necessary
OL,11,Fchanges are implemented as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible."
OL,14,FMr Hughes continued: "I understand
OL,15,Fthat parents, guardians, and students
OL,16,Fare seeking answers. However, please
OL,17,Fbe aware that there is an ongoing
OL,18,Fpolice investigation, and I must
OL,19,Fensure that any communication reflects
OL,20,Fthis appropriately.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
