OL,3,CSchool security reviewed after knife
OL,4,Cassault
OL,6,F"Some parents have shared concerns
OL,7,Fabout the timing and level of
OL,8,Fcommunication ... our immediate
OL,9,Fpriority was to ensure the safety and
OL,10,Fwellbeing of students and staff.
OL,12,F"I recognise that this initial
OL,13,Fcommunication was limited, and I
OL,14,Fapologise that I was unable to provide
OL,15,Fmore detail sooner.
OL,17,F"This process will be reviewed, and I
OL,18,Fam currently exploring best practice
OL,19,Fguidance used in UK schools to inform
OL,20,Fany future response."
