OL,6,FJersey Police will have officers at
OL,7,Fthe school for the rest of the week to
OL,8,Freassure everyone, while Mr Hughes
OL,9,Fexplained he is looking at what
OL,10,Ffurther support and training may be
OL,11,Fneeded for staff.
OL,13,FThe island's Education Minister,
OL,14,FDeputy Rob Ward, added: "I fully
OL,15,Funderstand that parents may feel
OL,16,Fanxious, but incidents of this nature
OL,17,Fare extremely rare.
OL,19,F"The school responded swiftly and
OL,20,Fprofessionally, and all students
OL,21,Fremained safe.
