OL,6,F"I want to reassure families that the
OL,7,Fschool will be open as normal and
OL,8,Fremains a safe environment for
OL,9,Flearning.
OL,11,F"All governmentfunded schools have
OL,12,Frobust sitesecurity measures in
OL,13,Fplace. These typically include
OL,14,Fcontrolled entry points, secure
OL,15,Fperimeter fencing, visitorsignin
OL,16,Fsystems, CCTV coverage, and routine
OL,17,Fmonitoring of school grounds.
